---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import meganImage from "../../assets/images/megan.png";
---

<Layout title="About | Offbeat Canine - Dog Training and Education">
    <div class="container py-10">
        <article class="prose lg:prose-xl dark:prose-invert mx-auto">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4">
                <div>
                    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">About</h1>
                    <p>
                        Thanks for taking the time to learn more what Offbeat
                        Canine is all about!
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <span class="font-display text-2xl">
                            I'm Megan, owner and training director!
                        </span>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start">
                    <div
                        class="group max-w-96 overflow-hidden flex flex-col items-start bg-white p-4 pb-12 shadow-md rounded-sm border border-neutral-200 rotate-2 transform transition-transform ease-out duration-300 hover:-rotate-2 hover:shadow-lg">
                        <Image
                            src={meganImage}
                            alt="Photo of Megan and her two dogs"
                            class="my-0 sm:my-0 md:my-0 lg:my-0"
                        />
                        <div
                            class="absolute h-full top-0 left-1/2 w-12 transform origin-top-left bg-gradient-to-l from-white/20 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:rotate-12 transition-all ease-out duration-300">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p>
                My journey into the world of dog training began over a decade
                ago when I embarked on my first job as a dog walker. It was
                during this time that I encountered a diverse array of canine
                companions, each with their own unique personalities and
                behaviors. From lively Vizslas to steadfast Dobermans, I found
                myself captivated by the intricacies of canine behavior and the
                deep bond between dogs and their humans.
            </p>
            <p>
                My passion for understanding and connecting with dogs led me to
                explore various avenues within the canine industry, from daycare
                facilities to rescue organizations. I've been lucky to work with
                and learn from some great people, further fueling my desire to
                pursue a career in dog training.
            </p>
            <p>
                Driven by a passion for continuous learning and growth, I
                pursued formal education at CATCH Canine Academy, where I honed
                my skills through a comprehensive curriculum. Combining my
                hands-on experience with theoretical knowledge, I've developed a
                holistic approach to dog training that prioritizes education and
                understanding.
            </p>
            <p>
                At Offbeat Canine Training, my mission is to revolutionize dog
                training by focusing on education. Just as humans invest in
                endless skill classes, I believe that dogs deserve the same
                level of education to thrive in their environments. I specialize
                in bridging the communication gap between dogs and their
                handlers, empowering humans to speak the language of their
                canine companions.
            </p>
            <p>
                My training tools are designed to be user-friendly, accompanied
                by a documented timeline of our progress with your dog. I offer
                personalized in-home sessions, starting with a comprehensive
                consultation, followed by a package tailored to meet your
                specific needs. With standardized pricing for standardized
                education, I ensure that every client receives the highest
                quality training experience.
            </p>
            <p>
                Join me on this journey to unlock the full potential of your dog
                and cultivate a harmonious bond based on mutual understanding
                and respect. Contact Offbeat Canine Training today to take the
                first step towards a brighter future with your furry friend!
            </p>
        </article>
    </div>
</Layout>
